title: Refrigerator LED Light Module
description: Refrigerator LED Light Module ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 40 Reviews PartSelect Number PS12070396 Manufacturer Part Number W11043011 This LED light is for refrigerators. The LED light attaches inside the cabinet and illuminates the inside of the refrigerator or freezer. Safely store any food that could deteriorate while the power is off and unplug the refrigerator before installing this part.

installationInstructions.author: Lynn from SAN JOSE, CA
installationInstructions.title: The LED light module in the refrigerator failed. Dim and one LED not lit
installationInstructions.content: There is a Philips head screw that holds the light cover on. Remove it. Pull the cover off from the back. It is rather tight so you need to pull fairly hard. Two tabs on the left side of the light hold the assembly in place. Release them and drop the module down. Unplug and do the reverse to put it back together.The manual says to unplug.the refrigerator. Power to the light can be turned off by taping the door switch down.
